4
00:02:01,987 --> 00:02:03,904
ZDRAVO.

5
00:02:03,905 --> 00:02:05,821
IZAÐI! BRZO! ŠTA? KO JE TO?

6
00:02:05,822 --> 00:02:08,218
BRŽE! ZAIME BOGA,
IZLAZI ODATLE! JA...

7
00:02:08,219 --> 00:02:10,135
